1. To add pages go to _posts directory. Name the pages with this format -> 2022-08-26-conv.md. [Date-TitleOfThePage.md] 
It will pop automatically at the end of the front page.

2. index.html - Front Page

3. _config.yml - this page consists of important settings.

4. _data/navigation.yml - consists of main links for index.html pages. 

5. hem-chandra.github.io/assets/css/main.scss - to change the color of URL link.

